## Branch and Commit Conventions

**Branch naming:**
- `feature/{game-slug}/{task-id}` â€” new feature tasks
- `fix/{game-slug}/{pr-number}` â€” bug fixes
- `live/{game-slug}/{short-description}` â€” live edits

